ces.md) — format specs, few-shot examples, chain-of-thought, sequential prompts, and constraints\n- [Vector Similarity Search](vector-similarity-search.md) — ANN algorithms (HNSW, IVF) for finding semantically similar content via embeddings\n- [Vector Databases](vector-databases.md) — specialized stores for embedding-based nearest-neighbor search\n- [Retrieval-Augmented Generation](retrieval-augmented-generation.md) — grounds LLM responses in retrieved documents via vector search\n\n## Evaluation & Quality\n\n- [Evaluator Super Agent](evaluator-super-agent.md) — automated prototype quality assessment (in progress)\n- [Agent Eval Harness](agent-eval-harness.md) — framework for evaluating AI skill quality\n- [Nielsen's Heuristics & The Jagged Edge](nielsens-heuristics-jagged-edge.md) — AI model comparison using usability heuristics\n\n## Tools & Skills\n\n- [Decision Kit](decision-kit.md) — Decision Driven Development toolkit\n- [My Cursor Claw](my-cursor-claw.md) — personal workspace with 20+ skills, 5 MCP connections, and automated daily review\n- [Skill Overlays](skill-overlays.md) — LLM-generated project-specific context files that improve agent accuracy\n\n## Daily Work Logs\n\n- [Cursor Work — 2026-06-16](cursor-work-2026-06-16.md) — trend-scan, critique, humanize-text, doc-sync, superpowers skills; GitHub README; second brain smart check-ins\n\n## Meetings\n\n- [Ansible AI Helpers Strategy — 2026-06-17](ansible-ai-helpers-strategy-2026-06-17.md) — heuristic eval pilot, centralized repo distribution via MRs, June 30 Ansible leadership pitch\n- [RH AI-First UX — 2026-06-18](rh-ai-first-ux-2026-06-18.md) — Fable AI impressions, GitLab pages fix, prototype-evaluate demo, Outcome Creator project plan, Jira migration\n- [Andy/Evan Eval Review — 2026-06-16](andy-evan-eval-review-2026-06-16.md) — outcomes grounding, super evaluator architecture, overlay approach confirmed\n- [Andy/Evan Meeting — 2026-06-22](andy-evan-2026-06-22.md) — eval scores improved (11→19), flagging system, Prototype Creator integration cost strategy\n- [Zack/Evan Meeting — 2026-06-24](zack-evan-2026-06-24.md) — Jira standardization, story points, skill architecture (context window limits)\n- [AI-First Sync — 2026-06-25](ai-first-sync-2026-06-25.md) — Evan's prototype evaluator presentation, 3.6 branch, readiness check discussion\n- [RH AI-First UX — 2026-06-25](rh-ai-first-ux-2026-06-25.md) — Outcome Creator JTBD integration, testing fragmentation, unified testing proposal\n- [WG: UXD Efficiency — 2026-06-29](wg-uxd-efficiency-2026-06-29.md) — AI helpers repo strategy, Archie rebranding, productivity skills repo, AI cost management\n- [Andy/Evan Meeting — 2026-06-29](andy-evan-2026-06-29.md) — evaluator progress, report UX, UXD PC7 cluster, sub-skill structure, Leaderboard of Pain\n- [Midpoint Check-in — 2026-06-30](midpoint-checkin-2026-06-30.md) — Zack's strengths/opportunities feedback, energy management framework, career direction, report-as-product challenge\n- [Weekly Design Sync — 2026-07-01](weekly-design-sync-2026-07-01.md) — evaluator demo prep, PatternFly 6 Q3 migration, Nielsen's heuristics as base rubric, scoring dimensions to revisit\n- [AI Helpers Repo Strategy Update — 2026-07-02](ai-helpers-repo-slack-2026-07-02.md) — Slack thread confirming skill directory structure, independent versioning, eval config policy (#uxd-rhoai)\n\n## Standups\n\n- [Standup — 2026-06-22](standup-2026-06-22.md) — sprint capacity adjustments, customer engagement strategy, Archie CLI update\n- [Standup — 2026-06-29](standup-2026-06-29.md) — usability testing RFC approved, UX debt prioritization for 3.5, research tooling updates\n\n## Session Logs\n\n- [Session Log — 2026-06-16](session-log-2026-06-16.md) — shipped second brain smart check-ins (importance, carry-forward, auto-resolve); created critique, humanize-text, doc-sync, superpowers, trend-scan skills; GitHub README redesign\n- [Session Log — 2026-06-15](session-log-2026-06-15.md) — built work-context, meeting-prep, standup-writer, session-log skills; sprint-manager skill; prototype-evaluate Slack response; progress doc update\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":23,"oldLines":6,"newStart":23,"newLines":7,"lines":[" "," - [Evaluator Super Agent](evaluator-super-agent.md) — automated prototype quality assessment (in progress)"," - [Agent Eval Harness](agent-eval-harness.md) — framework for evaluating AI skill quality","+- [Nielsen's 10 Usability Heuristics](nielsens-10-usability-heuristics.md) — canonical reference: all 10 heuristics with definitions, tips, and examples (Jakob Nielsen, 1994)"," - [Nielsen's Heuristics & The Jagged Edge](nielsens-heuristics-jagged-edge.md) — AI model comparison using usability heuristics"," "," ## Tools & Skills"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
