ated: prompt-engineering-best-practices.md — Core techniques: format specs, few-shot examples, chain-of-thought, sequential prompts, explicit constraints\n- Cross-linked with: agent-eval-harness.md, skill-overlays.md, evaluator-super-agent.md\n- Category: Machine Learning & AI\n\n## 2026-06-30 -- Ingested: Midpoint Check-in with Zack\n- Created: midpoint-checkin-2026-06-30.md -- Halfway internship review: strengths (pioneering work, collaborative curiosity, handling ambiguity), opportunities (bigger picture thinking, report as product), energy management framework, career direction\n- Cross-linked with: evaluator-super-agent.md, prototype-creator.md, ai-sdlc-pipeline.md\n- Category: Meetings\n- Note: Single-mic Gemini transcript, speakers reconstructed from context\n\n## 2026-06-29 -- Batch Ingestion: June 22-29 meetings + skill overlays\n\n**8 new wiki pages created:**\n\n1. **skill-overlays.md** -- LLM-generated project-specific context files (Carl Trieloff's team). Concept from Apr 2026, already showing accuracy gains.\n   - Cross-linked with: evaluator-super-agent.md, agent-eval-harness.md, my-cursor-claw.md, ai-sdlc-pipeline.md\n   - Category: Tools & Skills\n\n2. **andy-evan-2026-06-22.md** -- 1:1 review: eval scores improved 11→19, flagging system, Prototype Creator integration cost strategy ($25-30/run)\n   - Cross-linked with: evaluator-super-agent.md, prototype-creator.md, ux-quality-rubric.md, andy-evan-eval-review-2026-06-16.md\n   - Category: Meetings\n\n3. **standup-2026-06-22.md** -- Sprint capacity adjustments, customer engagement strategy, Archie CLI update\n   - Cross-linked with: prototype-creator.md, outcome-tiger-team.md, evaluator-super-agent.md\n   - Category: Standups (new)\n\n4. **zack-evan-2026-06-24.md** -- Jira standardization, story points (Fibonacci), skill architecture (11M token context limit hit)\n   - Cross-linked with: prototype-creator.md, evaluator-super-agent.md, ai-sdlc-pipeline.md, rfe-creator.md\n   - Category: Meetings\n\n5.